      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive excellence, maintained in pristine, showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from its original factory state. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak operational integrity. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a concours-level specimen that satisfies the most exacting standards of quality and performance.",
      "price": 46800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
